| Deliverable | Minimum data | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Notebook 03 | 1 month × 1 instrument | SHAP stability on ≥500k rows |
| Notebook 04 | 3 months × 2 instruments | 200 occurrences per cluster minimum |
| Notebook 05 | 1 week × 1 instrument | Queue sim is compute-bound |
| Notebook 06 | 3 months × 2 instruments | Multi-label classifier |
| Notebook 07 | 12 months × 4 instruments | Cascades rare; CPCV shrinks training set |
| UI §10.1 Triple View | single-day replay | Live panel |
| UI §10.2 Virtual order | single-day replay | Interactive one-order-at-a-time |
| UI §10.3 Pattern review | notebook 04 output | One-shot review session |
| UI §10.4 Correlation feed | notebook 06 output | Live inference |
| UI §10.5 Fragility gauge | notebook 07 output | Live FI stream |

Check current files in [p6-v2/data/](../../projects/p6-v2/data/) before
running. ES + NQ are the minimum symbol set; CL + GC unlock notebook 07
cross-instrument stress.

